»CL5:1. Introduction

»CL4:It will be a second party of this
kind here in our city »CL5:Szczecin». The
first one took place in 1992
organized by »CL5:SKYLIGHT» & »CL5:CRAZYBOYS»
(crap jakich malo) ... Let's take it
seriously, since '92 things have
changed, the water in Odra river has
been getting cleaner and cleaner,
many guys have died, the same amount
been born so we think it is a time to
show how a good party should look
like. 


»CL5:2. Rules»
The most important thing is that beer
and other digestive stuff will be
available at our well organized bar
so You won't be left alone in the
city of kid killers forced to feed
Your exhausted body. Anyway boozing
will be exterminated at the party
place. All kind of alcohol drinks,
drugs, knives, guns etc. will be
confiscated by our security guards.
We know that it's impossible to care
about all the 600 party people and a
small percent (very small) of
participants will get drunk. In this
case the security won't be so tough
and If You start to make mess, You or
Your body will be gently taken into a
safe place where You will be able to
get into the right mood. Now we are
serious, people who like to destroy,
who may not play with other children
could be even taken by the police so
behave yourself. 

»CL5:3. Where and when ?»

The party will took place in the
sport hall of The »CL5:ZESPOL SZKOL
BUDOWLANYCH» at the »CL5:Unislawy 32/33
street». If You want to know exact way
to  get here without trobles You will
be able to see a map in our final 
invitation which will be released at
»CL5:Gravity» party. Everything starts on
»CL5:7.XI.98» and finishes on »CL5:8.XI.98.»




»CL5:4. How much is the party ? »
The entrance fee will not exceed
»CL5:30PLN», people with their own
computers could pay a lower cost fee
(about »CL5:25PLN»). Foreginers, girls,
Marek Pampuch don't have to pay
anything. 

»CL5:5. Kkkompetitons»

Platforms:

»CL5:1.» AMiGA
