Wild i Crazy Demo compo, will be
joined together.
Music and GFX Compo will be executed
using Amiga.

»CL5:1. Equipment»
Amiga 4000/PPC604e/233Mhz +
060/50, 128MB RAM/CyberVisionPPC, 
Delphina DSP lite or Amiga 4000/060/
66Mhz/128MB RAM, CGFX3D, Delphina 
DSPlite if this does not make You 
feel happy we can use A1200/PPC603e
/240Mhz + 040/25Mhz/64MB RAM.

»CL5:Demo:» One production per group. 
Duration time is not determined. 
Exit to system on LMB. 
8 MB max. after compression. 
Amos or demomaniac demos will 
be shifted to crazy demo compo

»CL5:Intro 64K:» One production per group. 
Duration time is not determined. 
Exit to system on LMB. 
65536 bytes max. 
Amos or demomaniac demos will be 
shifted to crazy demo compo.

»CL5:Intro 4K:» One production for a coder.
Duration time is not determined. 
Exit to system on LMB. 
4096 bytes max. 

»CL5:4ch music:»
All the modules will be played with
a use of DigiBoosterPRO + 
DelphinaDSPlite. 
One module per musician. 
Duration time 8min.
Lenght 1MB max. 
Format: mod

»CL5:Multichannel:» All the modules will be
played with use of DigiBoosterPRO + 
DelphinDSPlite. 
One module per musicain. 
Duration time 8min.
Lenght 1MB max. 
Formats: mod(8-32), xm, ft, 
s3m, mmd0-3, dbm.

»CL5:THX music:» One module per musican. 
Duration time 3 min.

»CL5:Graphics:» One picture per graphician.
'photoshops' not allowed. 
Formats: iff, png, gif, jpg.

»CL5:Trace:» One trace per tracer. 
Traces with objects not by the author
of the trace will be thrown away.

»CL5:Crazy Demo:» Number of productions is
not limited, everything depends on 
Your synapses. 
We will try to play each production 
otherwise we will run our special 
selection committee.

